reviewText: This is another DVD of 2 great episodes of the Beverly Hillbillies, a must have DVD. Sandra K.

This tape is very poor quality. It has static and skips in the recording.
There was several in mine.

The picture and audio quality of the episodes on here is very good.  The only bad thing is the episodes don't contain the original theme music. However, they contain an instrumental version of "The Ballad of Jed Clampett".  If it weren't for the theme, I would have given it 5 stars
